## Public vs Private vs Protected

| Access Level | Same Class | Child Class (extends) | Outside Class |
|--------------|-----------|-----------------------|---------------|
| public       | ✔️        | ✔️                    | ✔️            |
| private      | ✔️        | ❌                    | ❌            |
| protected    | ✔️        | ✔️                    | ❌            |
